          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04591'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_116' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_84gc' title='Col. 84GC &mdash; HL Deb 27 February 2001 vol 622 c84GC' name='column_84gc' href='#column_84gc' rel='bookmark'>84GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04592'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_117' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
