        Clause 38 [<span class="italic">Reserve fund</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04621'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_146' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
