        <span class="member">Lord Whitty</span> moved Amendment No. 92:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04802'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_327' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
