      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04869'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_394' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Whitty</span> moved Amendment No. 99:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04870'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_395' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 30, line 13, leave out from ("company") to end of line 14
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04871'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_396' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04872'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_397' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 100 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04873'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_398' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Whitty</span> moved Amendment No. 101:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04874'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_399' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 30, leave out lines 17 to 25
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04875'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_400' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04876'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_401' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendments Nos. 102 to 107 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04877'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_402' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Whitty</span> moved Amendment No. 108:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04878'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_403' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 30, line 33, leave out ("1993 Act") and insert ("<a href="/acts/leasehold-reform-housing-and-urban-development-act-1993">Leasehold Reform, Housing and Urban Development Act 1993</a> (referred to in this Part as "the 1993 Act")
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04879'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_404' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        ( )"RTE company" has the same meaning as in Chapter I of Part I of the 1993 Act.").
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04880'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_405' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04881'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_406' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 70, as amended, agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0622P0-04882'>
        <a name='S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_407'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_407' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Whitty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-whitty" title="Mr John Whitty">Lord Whitty</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This may be a convenient moment for the Committee to adjourn until Thursday, I st March at 4 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0622P0-04883'>
        <a name='S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_408'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-william-goodhart' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_408' title='Link to this speech by Mr William Goodhart' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-william-goodhart" title="Mr William Goodhart">Lord Goodhart</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Before we adjourn, may I have some indication of the plan for the future? At the moment, we have only one further day for the Committee stage. We have dealt with the first 110 amendments in two days, but we have another 159 to deal with. Will the Government provide a second further day?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0622P0-04884'>
        <a name='S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_409'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_409' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Whitty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-whitty" title="Mr John Whitty">Lord Whitty</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            It is not a matter for me. It will have to be pursued through the usual channels. At the moment there are three days, and we will need to consider how far we have come.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0622P0-04885'>
        <a name='S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_410'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-caroline-cox' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_410' title='Link to this speech by Ms Caroline Cox' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-caroline-cox" title="Ms Caroline Cox">The Deputy Chairman of Committees</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Thursday, 1st March at 4 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0622P0-04886'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0622P0_20010227_GCR_411' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at eight o'clock.
      </p>
